nt of the rice water weevil's spread, and to investigate integrated pest management systems, including biological control to suppress their populations.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Montauban, Cecilia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mas, Maria", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wangensteen, Owen S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sarto I Monteys, V\u00edctor", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Forn\u00f3s, David Gisbert", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mola, Xavi Ferr\u00e9", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "L\u00f3pez-Baucells, Adri\u00e0", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/84f07c42707fd0fda0d700ad5d015f9a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/7355a0519b74964738f2d344b9d933c67dfbde2ddee2c7366abf033518cbeedd", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/XG732BGB", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/XG732BGB", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/60b51db2b63f460671841d643e0f9c98!/b333037-335507", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"pages": "105427", "title": "Crop Protection", "volume": "141"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/84f07c42707fd0fda0d700ad5d015f9a"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:XG